title: Bagel Dog Bed
description: 40-inch Black Bagel Pet Dog Bed by Majestic Pet Products. Outside Dimensions 40"L x 29"W / Inside Dimensions 30"L x 18"W / Bolster 9"H x 8"W / Cushion 8"H. Base made of waterproof 300/600 Denier, the bolster and cushion made of a 7-ounce. Poly/Cotton Twill, stuffed with a Premium High Loft Polyester Fiber Fil. Machine washable; wash warm, tumble dry low. (Large recommended for dogs 45 to 70-pound).
